---
description: Enforces vue-i18n usage and prohibits hardcoded UI strings.
globs:
  - "src/components/**/*.vue"
  - "src/app/**/*.vue"
alwaysApply: true
---

# i18n Rules

No hardcoded UI strings.

Use:
$t('key')
or
t('key')

Key format:
app.core.*
app.module.<module>.*
app.toast_notification.*
app.api_error.*

Every new key must exist in:
- en-US.json
- pl-PL.json---
alwaysApply: true
---
